snippet.title: I made a MASCOT HORROR Game IN ONE DAY...
snippet.description:
Today I'm showing you how I made my own MASCOT HORROR game in 24 hours. Mascot horror is a genre that makes a LOT of money, and I also wanna make some money so I thought I'd give it a try. This game was so fun to make and it took a lot of effort so please subscribe!

PLAY MY GAME FREE HERE:
Itch: https://realgoosestudios.itch.io/minced

Support me on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/RealGooseStudios
Follow my Instagram - @notgoosestudios
Join my discord - https://discord.gg/EcFBVTXhn5
Special thanks to Jex for the background gameplay! 
Check him out here: @jex714
